page.title: 16 COBTREE MANOR,MAIDSTONE
page.content: {Cobtree Manor Park}was once a private zoo and has recently been made into a place to walk, play, picnic or anything you like except picking the flowers and damaging the trees. It also has a{golf course}and this is very popular but most people come here to{walk}and enjoy being in the country. We often bring a picnic to eat after we have had our walk. There are many walks through both{woods}and {open countryside.}The park has a large {car-park}well screened by trees. It also has a{warden's office}and a {toilet block.}Everything else in the park is natural. Many people ride their horses in the park on a specially prepared track. My brother and I often play a chase game with my sisters here - it's good fun. by David Gilhespy
